# Frontend

## Components
- Small, focused components
- Typed props — never `any`
- Minimal state — lift logic out of components
- No business logic in components — call pure functions from features/

## Styling
- Plain CSS inside Plasmo Shadow DOM (via getStyle / data-text imports)
- No external UI library
- Tool-like, readable, lightweight design
- Neutral color scheme

## Extension
- Content script UI via Plasmo CSUI pattern
- Use PlasmoCSConfig for match patterns
- Use getShadowHostId for Shadow DOM control
- Use getStyle for CSS isolation
